* Schematic Name:                             gcd_seq, NgSpice Name: gcd_seq
.model u19 gcd_seq(rise_delay=1.0e-9 fall_delay=1.0e-9 input_load=1.0e-12 instance_id=1 ) 
* Schematic Name:                             adc_bridge_8, NgSpice Name: adc_bridge
.model u24 adc_bridge(in_low=0.8 in_high=1.2 rise_delay=1.0e-9 fall_delay=1.0e-9 ) 
* Schematic Name:                             adc_bridge_8, NgSpice Name: adc_bridge
